value.string: Want to invest in your Maui lifestyle? Is a great, close, be there in 5-15 minutes from everything location meaningful? Does collecting mail box income while you live-work-play sound good? How does, do nothing, move-in ready, resonate, certainly that’s important, right? Well guess what, there is a place, not in your dreams, but a live it everyday, “pinch me I’m there realty.” Of course you’ve heard it before, the famous “this property has potential,” now say it three times. Income, here’s some thoughts; owner/rental, manager/rental, owner-manager. Get on the phone! Call, text, email, your favorite Realtor for more info or to setup a private property viewing. Buyers agent please see Realtor Remarks for more details. TMK shows 3207 Hoomua, permits show 529 Mililani.

Over a half acre of land with unobstructed ocean views with multiple structures and generous rental income in place. Main home has 3 bedrooms and 2 baths upstairs and 2 studios downstairs. Ohana consists of 2 bedrooms and 1 bath with a large exterior lanai with ocean views. $7100/month rental income!!! Plenty of parking and privacy. Private road is owned in conjunction with neighboring property which is also for sale. Buy both properties and have over an acre in Maui Meadows. See listing 539 Kupulau Dr. MLS#366247. Buyer and buyer's agent to do own due diligence as to permits, inspections, conforming use.

3 bedroom 2 bath octagonal home with views from every angle plus a bonus studio below. Large wrap around lanai with panoramic ocean views and privacy. Photo voltaic already installed to cover electric bills. Large 1 bedroom 1 bath detached Ohana with ocean views. $4800/month rental income. Offered in conjunction with 541 Kupulau Dr. MLS#366246. This would give you over an acre of land and 4 PLUS structures in Maui Meadows. Excellent rental income producer. Buyer and Buyer's agent to do own due diligence as to permits, inspections and conforming use. EXCELLENT RENTAL INCOME!!!

This is a charming and bright single story cottage-like home in a cul-de-sac with ocean views and a separate 2 bedroom ohana. All this on a half acre with a neighbor only on one side. Wow. The home has had one owner for 27 years and been kept immaculately. Recent additions include wholly owned Photo Voltaic, 3 split-AC units that cool the house in minutes, 6 year old roofing on both the house and Ohana, and the cess pool was replaced with a septic system in 2009. The house and cottage exteriors have been painted. The back yard has about a third of the property unused so there's plenty of room for a pool, garden or back yard for kids. The house is close to Piilani Hwy for easy access, but far enough for no hwy noise. You'll want to see this delightful move-in ready home.

Well-maintained home on well-maintained half-acre Maui Meadows lot. House re-painted. Flooring and appliances have been replaced. Open beam ceiling in living and dining areas. Nice deck area to enjoy the sunsets from. Lots of space for a cottage. Close to one of Maui Meadows' entrances. With creativity (and money, of course) transform this Property into a place you will look forward to coming home to!!! Building permit has expired for unfinished swimming pool in back.

Amazing setting and views for this large, R-3 zoned & double-tiered lot with 1950s classic Kama'aina home. Panoramic vistas span from the West Maui Mountains to Kahului Harbor, the North Shore, Haleakala and the Central Valley below. The cozy and neat 3-bedroom / 2-bathroom, single level residence is situated on the top plateau, granting peace and privacy while enjoying the views. Wake-up to sunrise while you sip your morning coffee. Lovingly maintained by the original owners, the floor plan offers a spacious 2-car garage that could double-up as family room or storage / workshop, a utility bathroom by the entry foyer area with laundry, separate dining room and an enclosed patio towards the view. Recently installed spit-unit A/C and newer appliances. Mature sour-sop & mango trees in the backyard. The lower plateau of the lot already has a driveway access and could easily accommodate a second dwelling. There's lots of potential here and this is one-of-a-kind, rare opportunity! With its central location and proximity to schools, shopping, medical facilities and entertainment you may want to book your private showing today and check-it out for yourself. Buyers & Buyer's Agents to perform own due diligence at Maui County with regards to further development, subdivision or CPR potential. No CC&Rs. No Maintenance Fees. Showings by appointment only, do not disturb occupants. This house is not for rent.
